zones that the Icelandic\naverage melt ascent velocity during the last deglaciation is likely to be\n$\\sim100$ $\\mathrm{m/yr}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 2 Feb 2019 11:30:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 May 2019 11:24:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-16"}
